name: Perfectly Generic Object
description: It's a perfectly generic object in all respects. You feel absolutely nothing. And that's the point.

name: Shard of Everything
description: Every property, every purpose. Especially the ones you didn't ask for.

name: Rocket Pack
description: It's a jetpack. Use with caution, as it may cause you to fly into the sun or something.

name: Rocket Shoes
description: Jetpacks for your feet! Not approved by the FAA, but who cares about that? Not you, that's for sure.

name: Red Sucker
description: A large, bright red lollipop. Only one of it can exist at a time across all universes.

name: Green Sucker
description: A large, bright green lollipop. Only one of it can exist at a time across all universes.

name: Lollipop
description: It's just a lollipop. Maybe you should try OR instead of AND?

name: Spiral Sucker
description: A large lollipop with swirls of red and green. You are compelled to lick it....

name: Captchalogue Card
description: A card that can hold any item you captchalogue. Each item has a unique code that identifies it on the back.
